(60, 1, '2023-06-18 14:23:14', '2023-06-18 10:23:14', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Welcome!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":56,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/tem/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1600x1000_van_gogh_experience-1024x640.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-56\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Step into the captivating world of Vincent van Gogh, one of the most influential artists in history. Here, you will discover a treasure trove of information, insights, and appreciation for the life and works of this extraordinary Dutch painter.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":57,\"width\":737,\"height\":413,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/tem/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/images.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-57\" width=\"737\" height=\"413\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Immerse yourself in the vibrant colors, expressive brushstrokes, and profound emotions that define van Gogh\'s artistic style. Explore his iconic masterpieces, from the swirling night sky in \"Starry Night\" to the radiant sunflowers in bloom. Uncover the stories behind his art, the inspiration that fueled his creativity, and the profound impact he left on the art world.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whether you\'re an art enthusiast, a Van Gogh admirer, or simply curious about the artistic journey of a true visionary, this page is designed to be your gateway to the captivating world of Vincent van Gogh. Join us on this artistic odyssey and delve into the brilliance and brilliance of one of art history\'s greatest minds.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Experience the art, the passion, and the enduring legacy of Vincent van Gogh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":59,\"width\":365,\"height\":486,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8888/tem/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/125399-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-59\" width=\"365\" height=\"486\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->', 'home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-06-18 14:23:14', '2023-06-18 10:23:14', '', 5, 'http://localhost:8888/tem/?p=60', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
